These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-8-1::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: mauve, emerald, light-blue
1. the person who likes mauve is on the far right##1
2. the person who likes mauve is not to the left of the person who likes emerald##8
3. the person who likes light-blue is somewhere to the left of the person who likes emerald##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |    2    |    3     |
| Color   | light-blue | emerald | mauve |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-8-2::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: light-blue, aquamarine, orange
1. the person who likes orange is not to the left of the person who likes light-blue##8
2. the person who likes orange is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1   |   2    |     3     |
| Color   | light-blue | orange | aquamarine |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-8-3::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  lawyer, dancer, chef
1. the dancer is on the left of the lawyer##1
2. the lawyer is not to the right of the chef##8

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2   |  3  |
| Job   | dancer | lawyer | chef |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-8-4::.
