1. the person eating asparagus is not to the left of the person eating pumpkin##8
2. the person eating nectarine is on the right of the person eating asparagus##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |  2   |      3      |
| Food   | pumpkin | asparagus | nectarine |

