.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-8-5::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: juice, soy-milk, mirinda
1. the person drinking soy-milk is in an even position##4
2. the person drinking soy-milk is not to the right of the person drinking mirinda##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |     3     |
| Beverage   | juice | soy-milk | mirinda |

