.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-8-9::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: november, january, july
1. the person who's birthday is in july is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in november##8
2. the person who's birthday is in november is between the person who's birthday is in january and the person who's birthday is in july##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2   |  3   |
| Birthday   | january | november | july |

